    {
      "id": "s1-18",
      "sectionId": "s1",
      "title": "配置文件",
      "kind": "text",
      "body": "Glances 的配置文件位于 `~/.config/glances/glances.conf`。通过编辑这个文件，可以自定义 Glances 的显示和行为。"
    },
    {
      "id": "s1-19",
      "sectionId": "s1",
      "title": "配置文件",
      "kind": "text",
      "body": "#### 例子配置文件"
    },
    {
      "id": "s1-20",
      "sectionId": "s1",
      "title": "配置文件",
      "kind": "code",
      "lang": "ini",
      "code": "[global]\nrefresh=2      # 设置刷新间隔（以秒为单位）\n\n[alert]\nenable = True\n\n# 邮件告警配置（放在 alert 下）\nmail = True\nmail_from = \nmail_to = \nmail_server = \nmail_port = 465\nmail_user = \nmail_password = \nmail_tls = True\n\n[cpu]\nenable=true    # 显示 CPU 负载平均值\n[mem]\nenable=true    # 显示内存使用情况\n[disk]\nenable=true    # 显示磁盘 I/O 信息\n[network]\nenable=true    # 显示网络带宽使用情况"
    },
    {
      "id": "s1-21",
      "sectionId": "s1",
      "title": "Web 访问",
      "kind": "code",
      "lang": "sh",
      "code": "# 使用 Glances 的 API：\nglances -w\n# 访问 API：\ncurl http://<your_ip>:61208/api/3/all"
    },
    {
      "id": "s1-22",
      "sectionId": "s1",
      "title": "Web 访问",
      "kind": "text",
      "body": "**使用 Docker 部署 Glances**："
