    {
      "id": "s4-100",
      "sectionId": "s4",
      "title": "位置",
      "kind": "text",
      "body": "您可以将自己的 `glances.conf` 文件放在以下位置："
    },
    {
      "id": "s4-101",
      "sectionId": "s4",
      "title": "位置",
      "kind": "text",
      "body": ":-- | -- | --\n:-- | -- | --\n`Linux`, `SunOS` | ~/.config/glances/, /etc/glances/, /usr/share/docs/glances/ |\n`*BSD` |~/.config/glances/, /usr/local/etc/glances/, /usr/share/docs/glances/ |\n`macOS` | ~/Library/Application Support/glances/, /usr/local/etc/glances/, /usr/share/docs/glances/ |\n`Windows` | %APPDATA%\\glances\\glances.conf |"
    },
    {
      "id": "s4-102",
      "sectionId": "s4",
      "title": "位置",
      "kind": "text",
      "body": "---"
    },
    {
      "id": "s4-103",
      "sectionId": "s4",
      "title": "位置",
      "kind": "text",
      "body": "• 在 Windows XP 上，%APPDATA% 为：`C:\\Documents and Settings\\<USERNAME>\\Application Data`\n• 在 Windows Vista 及更高版本上：`C:\\Users\\<用户名>\\AppData\\Roaming`"
    },
    {
      "id": "s4-104",
      "sectionId": "s4",
      "title": "语法",
      "kind": "code",
      "lang": "ini",
      "code": "[global]\n# 刷新率（默认为至少 2 秒）\n# 可以通过 -t <sec> 选项覆盖\n# 也可以在每个插件部分覆盖它\nrefresh=2\n# Glances 是否应该检查 PyPI 上是否有更新的版本？\ncheck_update=false\n# 历史大小（最大值数）\n# 默认值为28800：1天，每3秒1分\nhistory_size=28800"
    },
    {
      "id": "s4-105",
      "sectionId": "s4",
      "title": "CPU 插件的示例",
      "kind": "code",
      "lang": "ini",
      "code": "[cpu]\ndisable=False\nrefresh=3\nuser_careful=50\nuser_warning=70\nuser_critical=90\niowait_careful=50\niowait_warning=70\niowait_critical=90\nsystem_careful=50\nsystem_warning=70\nsystem_critical=90\nsteal_careful=50\nsteal_warning=70\nsteal_critical=90"
    },
    {
      "id": "s4-106",
      "sectionId": "s4",
      "title": "InfluxDB 导出模块",
      "kind": "code",
      "lang": "ini",
      "code": "[influxdb]\n# 配置 --export influxdb 选项\n# https://influxdb.com/\nhost=localhost\nport=8086\nuser=root\npassword=root\ndb=glances\nprefix=localhost\n#tags=foo:bar,spam:eggs"
    },
    {
      "id": "s4-107",
      "sectionId": "s4",
      "title": "Nginx AMP",
      "kind": "code",
      "lang": "ini",
      "code": "[amp_nginx]\n# 应启用 Nginx 状态页面 \n# https://easyengine.io/tutorials/nginx/status-page/\n\nenable=true\nregex=\\/usr\\/sbin\\/nginx\nrefresh=60\none_line=false\nstatus_url=http://localhost/nginx_status"
    },
    {
      "id": "s5-108",
      "sectionId": "s5",
      "title": "CSV",
      "kind": "code",
      "lang": "sh",
      "code": "$ glances --export csv \\\n   --export-csv-file /tmp/glances.csv \\\n   --quiet"
    },
    {
      "id": "s5-109",
      "sectionId": "s5",
      "title": "CSV",
      "kind": "text",
      "body": "可以将统计数据导出到 CSV 文件"
    },
    {
      "id": "s5-110",
      "sectionId": "s5",
      "title": "JSON",
      "kind": "code",
      "lang": "sh",
      "code": "$ glances --export json \\\n   --export-json-file /tmp/glances.json"
    },
    {
      "id": "s5-111",
      "sectionId": "s5",
      "title": "JSON",
      "kind": "text",
      "body": "可以将统计信息导出到 JSON 文件"
    },
    {
      "id": "s5-112",
      "sectionId": "s5",
      "title": "Cassandra",
      "kind": "text",
      "body": "您可以将统计数据导出到 Cassandra 或 Scylla 服务器"
    },
    {
      "id": "s5-113",
      "sectionId": "s5",
      "title": "Cassandra",
      "kind": "code",
      "lang": "ini",
      "code": "[cassandra]\nhost=localhost\nport=9042\nprotocol_version=3\nkeyspace=glances\nreplication_factor=2\ntable=localhost"
    },
    {
      "id": "s5-114",
      "sectionId": "s5",
      "title": "Cassandra",
      "kind": "text",
      "body": "并运行 Glances："
    },
    {
      "id": "s5-115",
      "sectionId": "s5",
      "title": "Cassandra",
      "kind": "code",
      "lang": "sh",
      "code": "$ glances --export cassandra"
    },
    {
      "id": "s5-116",
      "sectionId": "s5",
      "title": "Cassandra",
      "kind": "text",
      "body": "数据模型如下："
    },
    {
      "id": "s5-117",
      "sectionId": "s5",
      "title": "Cassandra",
      "kind": "code",
      "lang": "sql",
      "code": "CREATE TABLE <table> (plugin text, time timeuuid, stat map<text,float>, PRIMARY KEY (plugin, time))"
    },
    {
      "id": "s5-118",
      "sectionId": "s5",
      "title": "Graph",
      "kind": "code",
      "lang": "ini",
      "code": "[graph]\n# --export graph 选项的配置\n# 设置创建图形（.svg 文件）的路径\n# 可以通过 --graph-path 命令行选项覆盖\npath=/tmp\n# 可以通过设置自动生成图表\n# generate_every 为一个非零值，对应于之间的秒数\n# 两代。将其设置为 0 以禁用图形自动生成。\ngenerate_every=60\n# 请参阅 Pygal lib 文档中的以下配置键定义\n# http://pygal.org/en/stable/documentation/index.html\nwidth=800\nheight=600\nstyle=DarkStyle"
    },
    {
      "id": "s5-119",
      "sectionId": "s5",
      "title": "Graph",
      "kind": "text",
      "body": "并运行 Glances："
    },
    {
      "id": "s5-120",
      "sectionId": "s5",
      "title": "Graph",
      "kind": "code",
      "lang": "sh",
      "code": "$ glances --export graph \\\n      --export-graph-path /tmp"
    },
    {
      "id": "s5-121",
      "sectionId": "s5",
      "title": "CouchDB",
      "kind": "text",
      "body": "您可以将统计数据导出到 CouchDB 服务器"
