    {
      "id": "s5-125",
      "sectionId": "s5",
      "title": "InfluxDB",
      "kind": "text",
      "body": "您可以将统计数据导出到 InfluxDB 服务器（时间序列服务器）"
    },
    {
      "id": "s5-126",
      "sectionId": "s5",
      "title": "InfluxDB",
      "kind": "text",
      "body": "测量 | 字段 | 标签\n:-- | -- | --\ncpu | user system iowait… |  hostname\nnetwork | read_bytes write_bytes time_since_update…  | hostname disk_name\ndiskio | rx tx time_since_update…  | hostname interface_name\ndocker | cpu_percent memory_usage…  | hostname name\ngpu | proc mem temperature…  | hostname gpu_id\n<!--rehype:className=show-header-->"
    },
    {
      "id": "s5-127",
      "sectionId": "s5",
      "title": "InfluxDB",
      "kind": "text",
      "body": "#### InfluxDB （最高版本 1.7.x）"
    },
    {
      "id": "s5-128",
      "sectionId": "s5",
      "title": "InfluxDB",
      "kind": "code",
      "lang": "ini",
      "code": "[influxdb]\nhost=localhost\nport=8086\nprotocol=http\nuser=root\npassword=root\ndb=glances\n# 所有测量名称都会添加前缀\n# Ex: prefix=foo\n#     => foo.cpu\n#     => foo.mem\n# 您还可以使用动态值\n#prefix=foo\n# 将为所有测量添加以下标签\n# 您还可以使用动态值\n# 注意：主机名始终作为标签添加\n#tags=foo:bar,spam:eggs,domain:`domainname`"
    },
    {
      "id": "s5-129",
      "sectionId": "s5",
      "title": "InfluxDB",
      "kind": "text",
      "body": "并运行 Glances："
    },
    {
      "id": "s5-130",
      "sectionId": "s5",
      "title": "InfluxDB",
      "kind": "code",
      "lang": "sh",
      "code": "$ glances --export influxdb"
    },
    {
      "id": "s5-131",
      "sectionId": "s5",
      "title": "InfluxDB",
      "kind": "text",
      "body": "#### InfluxDB v2（来自 InfluxDB v1.8.x/Flux 和 InfluxDB v2.x）"
    },
    {
      "id": "s5-132",
      "sectionId": "s5",
      "title": "InfluxDB",
      "kind": "code",
      "lang": "ini",
      "code": "[influxdb2]\nhost=localhost\nport=8086\nprotocol=http\norg=nicolargo\nbucket=glances\ntoken=EjFUTWe8U-MIseEAkaVIgVnej_TrUpDy==\n# 设置两个导出之间的间隔（以秒为单位）\n# 如果时间间隔设置为 0，\n# 则使用 Glances 刷新时间（默认行为）\n#interval=0\n# 将为所有测量名称添加前缀\n# Ex: prefix=foo\n#     => foo.cpu\n#     => foo.mem\n# 您还可以使用动态值\n#prefix=foo\n# 将为所有测量添加以下标签\n# 您还可以使用动态值.\n# 注意：主机名始终作为标签添加\n#tags=foo:bar,spam:eggs,domain:`domainname`"
    },
    {
      "id": "s5-133",
      "sectionId": "s5",
      "title": "InfluxDB",
      "kind": "text",
      "body": "并运行 Glances："
